### HomeGuru Stats API - Examples
### Примеры запросов к API для тестирования

### 1. Root endpoint - проверка работоспособности
GET http://localhost:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get stats for last week (default)
GET http://localhost:8000/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Get stats for last day (24 hours)
GET http://localhost:8000/stats?period=day
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get stats for last week (7 days)
GET http://localhost:8000/stats?period=week
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Get stats for last month (30 days)
GET http://localhost:8000/stats?period=month
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Invalid period (should return 422 error)
GET http://localhost:8000/stats?period=invalid
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. OpenAPI schema
GET http://localhost:8000/openapi.json
Accept: application/json

###

### 9. API Documentation (Swagger UI)
### Open in browser: http://localhost:8000/docs

### 10. Alternative API Documentation (ReDoc)
### Open in browser: http://localhost:8000/redoc

###

### ============================================================================
### Chat API Examples
### ============================================================================

### 11. Authenticate as admin
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Response will contain JWT token for admin access

###

### 12. Send message in normal mode (HomeGuru)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Привет! Помоги мне с дизайном спальни",
  "mode": "normal",
  "session_id": "test-session-123"
}

###

### 13. Send message in admin mode (Statistics)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Сколько всего пользователей в системе?",
  "mode": "admin",
  "session_id": "test-session-123"
}

### Response will include SQL query used

###

### 14. Get chat history for session
GET http://localhost:8000/api/chat/history?session_id=test-session-123
Accept: application/json

###

### 15. Clear chat history for session
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/clear
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "test-session-123"
}

###

